    "description": "<p>Guaranteed reaction. <br />For one round, you may attempt a Defense roll at –10% to defend an adjacent ally or against ranged attacks passing through adjacent hexes.</p><hr /><p>Using Guard cancels Defensive Stance.<br />Effects that cancel Aiming or Stances on either the protected target or the protector cancel Guard. <br />If you were to lose more Reactions than you currently have, Guard is canceled.</p>",
